<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-04-0216 </DOCNO><TEXT>Since the amendment of the Clean Air Technnical Guide (TA-Luft), measuresto reduce emission are also necessary in furnaces with a capacity ofless than 50 megawatts. Essentially, the proportions of dust, nitrogenoxide and sulphur dioxide in flue gas must be reduced. Basically, thereis the possibility of using fuels with less pollutant content or of reducingthe pollutant emission by technical means.</TEXT></DOC>